title.narrative: Fund Cite: FY16 Program Activities: Skopje, Macdon. Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services - Other Contractual Services NOC (A, B, C) (ITA) (INS) (FAS). SINLEC16YUHA INCLE funds prog assis to BLTS &HCG. ATA EAJO15CRT01 KEN TANZ and UGANDA CRT 3. SURCHARGE FOR PR5721601

description.narrative: Combat transnational terrorism, especially from al-Qa'ida, its affiliates, and adherents using a strategic counterterrorism approach that focuses on 1) countering violent extremism; 2) building the capacity of civilian law enforcement and criminal justice institutions to address threats within their own borders; and 3) building stronger relationships with our partners around the world – in order to engage in a broader, more comprehensive counterterrorism effort that treats civilian institutions, to include the justice sector and law enforcement, as a critical part of building effective partner capacity to counter terrorism.

This award strives to combat transnational terrorism, counter violent extremism, build the capacity of civilian law enforcement and criminal justice institutuions, and build stronger relationships with our partners around the world. This includes NON-PROLIFERATION[Covers miscellaneous contractual services not otherwise classified under Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services.]. Covers miscellaneous contractual services not otherwise classified under Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services.. Fund Cite: FY16 Program Activities: Chisinau, Moldova[Covers miscellaneous contractual services such as A&E contracts and IT site preparation by the PBA, GSA, and commercial contracts, among other things.]. Fund Cite: FY16 Program Activities: Chisinau, Moldova[Covers miscellaneous contractual services not otherwise classified under Miscellaneous/Other Contractual Services.]. NON-PROLIFERATION[Covers the costs of miscellaneous travel related contractual expenses paid on travel vouchers. (Discontinued as of 12/27/2015) (Use 2163)].
